<title>Heritage Listserv Application -- Heritage</title>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/heritage/paperh.jpg"><center><img src="/heritage/thf_log2.gif"></a><h3><font size="+1">H</font>eritage <font size="+1">I</font>nternet <font size="+1">U</font>pdate </h3></center>
<p>
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; Sign up here for the <b><font size="+1">H</font>eritage <font size="+1">I</font>nternet <font size="+1">U</font>pdate</b>, a weekly email report detailing <b>what's new</b> at Heritage! You will receive a listing of the latest Heritage policy papers available on our web site, and we'll alert you to new features and exclusive content only available on the Internet. For example, you'll get to preview some of the amusing and informative <b>Top 10 Facts</b> we assemble each week.  
<p><ul>
<li>We'll also give advanced notice for Heritage lectures, panel discussions, and Third Generation meetings.
<P>
<li>We will be adding additional features to this listserv in the near future, so check back soon for new lists.
<p>
<li>Want to stay on top of the issues? Sign up for the <b><font size="+1">H</font>eritage <font size="+1">I</font>nternet <font size="+1">U</font>pdate</b>.
</ul><P>
Select the list you'd like to join by clicking in the appropriate box, fill in the information below, and click the "Sign me up!" button below.  That's all there is to it!
<p><center>
