<H1><CENTER>Discovery Institute Inquiry</CENTER>
</H1>
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="rwbline2.gif" WIDTH="512" HEIGHT="6" ALIGN="BOTTOM"
NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"></CENTER>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P><CENTER><B>Discovery Institute Inquiry is published periodically throughout
the year. Each issue is a research paper by a Discovery Fellow or staff
member, and deals with a specific public policy issue.</B></CENTER>
